And yeah, it blew up.

00:12:15.560 --> 00:12:20.160
He said, we should be coming down

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:24.640
wherever the river was, the Pacific or the Atlantic or what.

00:12:24.640 --> 00:12:29.240
And bombs would be, he said, they'd be shipped on fire

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:32.600
each side of him, you know, and they'd be going through.

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:34.920
Oh, God, he said it was terrible.

00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:38.200
Because I know a lot of my friends off their father's.

00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:42.520
Well, Laura was saying about her brother and.

