Went to Aberadwe, number day.

00:13:25.880 --> 00:13:27.040
Yeah.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:33.120
And. Oh, God, I went to my mother and I came back.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:35.000
A lot of us went.

00:13:35.640 --> 00:13:39.960
I mean, it was you got more prejudice going into Cardiff

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:43.040
and once you were at the bay.

